+# Trainer-Toolbox Host Guide
+
+## Getting Started
+
+### Creating Your Account
+
+1. Go to your Trainer-Toolbox URL (e.g., `quiz2-1a35d.firebaseapp.com`)
+2. Click **Get Started** or **Sign Up**
+3. Enter your name, email, and password
+4. You'll be redirected to your **Host Dashboard**
+
+### Dashboard Overview
+
+Your dashboard is the central hub for managing classes, tools, and activities. From here you can:
+
+- Create and manage classes
+- Launch interactive tools
+- View student progress and leaderboards
+- Access your quiz library
+
+---
+
+## Managing Classes
+
+### Creating a Class
+
+1. From the Dashboard, click **Create Class**
+2. Give your class a name (e.g., "Morning Training Session")
+3. A unique **class code** will be generated automatically
+4. Share the code with participants so they can join
+
+### Viewing Class Members
+
+- Navigate to your class from the Dashboard
+- Click **Students** to see all enrolled members
+- You can view individual scores, attendance, and engagement data
+
+### Class Activity Feed
+
+Each class has a live activity feed showing current and recent activities.
+
+---
+
+## Interactive Tools
+
+### Quiz Battle
+
+Create competitive quizzes with multiple-choice questions.
+
+**Creating a Quiz:**
+1. Go to **Quiz Battle** from the Dashboard or Host Menu
+2. Click **Create New Quiz**
+3. Add questions with up to 4 answer options each
+4. Set time limits and point values per question
+5. Mark the correct answer for each question
+6. Save your quiz to the library
+
+**Running a Quiz:**
+1. Select a quiz from your **Library**
+2. A lobby will be created with a join code
+3. Share the join code with participants
+4. Click **Start** when everyone has joined
+5. Questions display one at a time on the host screen
+6. Participants answer on their devices in real-time
+7. Results show after each question and at the end
+
+### Live Polling
+
+Create instant polls to gauge opinions or check understanding.
+
+1. Go to **Poll** from the Host Menu
+2. Enter your poll question
+3. Add 2-4 answer options
+4. Launch the poll
+5. Watch responses come in live
+6. Results display as a bar chart in real-time
+
+### Word Storm (Word Cloud)
+
+Collect responses and display them as a live word cloud.
+
+1. Go to **Word Storm** from the Host Menu
+2. Enter a prompt or question
+3. Launch the session
+4. Participants submit words or short phrases
+5. Submissions appear as a growing word cloud
+6. Larger words indicate more frequent submissions
+
+### Tickr (Ticker/Marquee)
+
+Display scrolling messages from participants on screen.
+
+1. Go to **Tickr** from the Host Menu
+2. Launch a Tickr session
+3. Participants submit messages
+4. Messages scroll across the projected screen
+5. Great for Q&A sessions, shoutouts, or icebreakers
+
+### Randomizer
+
+Randomly select a student from your class.
+
+1. Go to **Randomizer** from the Host Menu
+2. Select your class
+3. Click **Spin the Wheel**
+4. The randomizer cycles through students with animation
+5. A winner is announced with celebratory effects
+6. Click **Spin Again** to select another student
+
+### Buzzer
+
+First-to-buzz-in tool for competitive activities.
+
+1. Go to **Buzzer** from the Host Menu
+2. Launch a buzzer session
+3. Participants see a buzzer button on their devices
+4. The first person to press the buzzer is identified
+5. A leaderboard tracks who buzzed in and when
+
+### Coin Flip
+
+Simple coin flip tool for decision-making or games.
+
+### Dice Roll
+
+Roll virtual dice with customizable sides.
+
+### Commitment Wall
+
+Participants post commitment notes that display on a shared wall.
+
+---
+
+## PicPick (Photo Contests)
+
+### Creating a Gallery
+
+1. Go to **PicPick** from the Dashboard
+2. Click **Create Gallery**
+3. Set up your gallery with a name and description
+4. A unique gallery code is generated
+5. Share the code with participants
+
+### Running a Contest
+
+1. Participants join using the gallery code
+2. They upload photos based on your prompt
+3. Voting begins when you enable it
+4. Results display in real-time
+
+---
+
+## Designer Studio (Workbooks)
+
+Create interactive workbooks for self-paced learning.
+
+1. Go to **Designer Studio** from the Host Menu
+2. Click **Create New Album**
+3. Add pages with text, images, and questions
+4. Set point values for completion
+5. Publish when ready
+6. Assign to classes for student access
+
+---
+
+## Leaderboard & Gamification
+
+### Leader Grid
+
+Track student engagement and scores across all activities.
+
+- Points accumulate from quizzes, polls, and other activities
+- Badges can be awarded for achievements
+- QR codes can be generated for scanning-based point awards
+
+### Badges
+
+Create and award custom badges to recognize achievements.
+
+### Parking Lot
+
+A space for students to "park" questions or topics for later discussion.
+
+---
+
+## Tips for Hosts
+
+- **Test before class**: Run through your activities before the session
+- **Share codes clearly**: Display join codes on the projector
+- **Use the projector view**: Many tools have a dedicated projector/display mode
+- **Check the class code**: Students need the code to join your class
+- **Monitor engagement**: Watch the live feed to see participation levels
+
+---
+
+## Troubleshooting
+
+**Students can't join:**
+- Verify the class code is correct
+- Ensure students are on the correct URL
+- Check that the activity is currently running
+
+**Activity not loading:**
+- Refresh the page
+- Check your internet connection
+- Try logging out and back in
+
+**Quiz not starting:**
+- Ensure at least one player has joined the lobby
+- Check that all questions have correct answers marked
+
+---
+
+## Support
+
+For technical issues, contact your Trainer-Toolbox administrator.
