+# Trainer-Toolbox Student Guide
+
+## Getting Started
+
+### Joining a Class
+
+1. Go to your Trainer-Toolbox URL
+2. Click **Join** or enter the URL provided by your instructor
+3. Enter the **class code** shared by your host
+4. Create your profile with a display name
+5. You'll be added to the class automatically
+
+### Your Dashboard
+
+Once enrolled, your Student Dashboard shows:
+
+- Active classes you've joined
+- Current activities and sessions
+- Your score and ranking
+- Available workbooks and assignments
+
+---
+
+## Participating in Activities
+
+### Quiz Battle
+
+1. Your host will share a quiz join code
+2. Enter the code to join the quiz lobby
+3. Wait for the host to start the quiz
+4. When a question appears, select your answer before time runs out
+5. Points are awarded for correct answers (faster answers earn more points)
+6. Your score and ranking update after each question
+7. Final results show at the end of the quiz
+
+### Live Polling
+
+1. When a poll is active, you'll see the question on your device
+2. Select your answer from the options provided
+3. Your response is counted immediately
+4. Results display on the host's screen in real-time
+
+### Word Storm
+
+1. When a Word Storm session is active, you'll see a text input
+2. Type a word or short phrase related to the prompt
+3. Submit your response
+4. Your submission appears in the live word cloud on screen
+
+### Tickr
+
+1. When a Tickr session is running, you'll see a message input
+2. Type your message or question
+3. Submit it to have it scroll across the projected display
+4. Great for asking questions during presentations
+
+### Buzzer
+
+1. When a buzzer round starts, you'll see a large buzzer button
+2. Press the buzzer as fast as you can when prompted
+3. The fastest person to buzz in is announced
+4. Wait for the next round
+
+---
+
+## Workbooks
+
+### Completing Workbooks
+
+1. Go to **Workbooks** from your Student Dashboard
+2. Open an assigned workbook
+3. Read through each page
+4. Answer any questions embedded in the workbook
+5. Navigate between pages using the page controls
+6. Completion earns bonus points
+
+---
+
+## PicPick (Photo Contests)
+
+### Joining a Gallery
+
+1. Go to **PicPick** from the main page
+2. Enter the gallery code provided by your host
+3. Upload a photo when prompted
+4. Vote on other participants' photos when voting opens
+
+---
+
+## Points & Rewards
+
+### Earning Points
+
+You earn points through various activities:
+
+- Answering quiz questions correctly
+- Participating in polls and word storms
+- Completing workbooks
+- Scanning QR badges
+- Winning special activities
+
+### Leaderboard
+
+- Your class has a live leaderboard showing rankings
+- Points accumulate across all activities
+- Check your position on the Student Dashboard
+
+### Redeeming Rewards
+
+If your host has set up a rewards system:
+
+1. Go to **Redeem** from your Dashboard
+2. Browse available rewards
+3. Select a reward to redeem your points
+
+---
+
+## Profile
+
+### Updating Your Profile
+
+1. Click on your **Profile** icon
+2. Update your display name
+3. Change your profile picture
+4. View your activity history and total points
+
+---
+
+## Tips
+
+- **Stay connected**: Keep your device connected to the internet during activities
+- **Be quick**: In Quiz Battle, faster correct answers earn more points
+- **Participate actively**: Many activities reward participation
+- **Check your dashboard**: New activities and assignments appear here
+
+---
+
+## Troubleshooting
+
+**Can't find the activity:**
+- Make sure you're in the correct class
+- Ask your host for the activity join code
+- Refresh your browser
+
+**Quiz answer not submitting:**
+- Check your internet connection
+- Make sure the timer hasn't expired
+- Try refreshing and rejoining
+
+**Points not updating:**
+- Points may take a moment to sync
+- Refresh your dashboard
+- Contact your host if the issue persists
+
+---
+
+## Support
+
+If you're having trouble, ask your host/instructor for help. They can assist with class codes, account issues, and activity access.
